      "num": "01 · the shape",
      "heading": "Humans should not have to remember every guardrail",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">If every team has to rediscover safe headers, secret handling, auth checks, logging rules, and dependency policy, security becomes a memory test.</p>"
        },
